      "writtenOn": "2021-03-18T23:39:34Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "At this point GrAA::kNo means the rect is axis aligned.\n\nWe need the check because blurs call fillRectToRect, which runs into http://skbug.com/11756 if we use GrFillRRectOp. (It\u0027s also slower to use dual source blending, or worse, dst reads).\n\nAdded a comment.",
      "parentUuid": "ba9afc5b_507eb66e",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 727,
        "startChar": 8,
        "endLine": 727,
        "endChar": 24
      },
      "revId": "24bf9efc41528e80bf3ab8cc692aaaa1b92bde9b",
